works.description: “My published post, “Khloe Kardashian Responds to Love Child Allegations", is infringed by the text excerpted on the site, beginning with the text "The Kardashians keep their fingers on a keypad 24 hours a day, just in case they need to Tweet a photo of their nail polish or remind you to go buy some more K-Krap."
